26#include "config.h"
27
28#include "CachedTextTrack.h"
29
30#include "CachedResourceClient.h"
31#include "CachedResourceClientWalker.h"
32#include "CachedResourceLoader.h"
33#include "SharedBuffer.h"
34#include "TextResourceDecoder.h"
35
36namespace WebCore {
37
38CachedTextTrack::CachedTextTrack(CachedResourceRequest&& request, PAL::SessionID sessionID, const CookieJar* cookieJar)
39 : CachedResource(WTFMove(request), Type::TextTrackResource, sessionID, cookieJar)
40{
41}
42
43void CachedTextTrack::doUpdateBuffer(SharedBuffer* data)
44{
45 ASSERT(dataBufferingPolicy() == DataBufferingPolicy::BufferData);
46 m_data = data;
47 setEncodedSize(data ? data->size() : 0);
48
49 CachedResourceClientWalker<CachedResourceClient> walker(m_clients);
50 while (CachedResourceClient* client = walker.next())
51 client->deprecatedDidReceiveCachedResource(*this);
52}
53
54void CachedTextTrack::updateBuffer(SharedBuffer& data)
55{
56 doUpdateBuffer(&data);
57 CachedResource::updateBuffer(data);
58}
59
60void CachedTextTrack::finishLoading(SharedBuffer* data, const NetworkLoadMetrics& metrics)
61{
62 doUpdateBuffer(data);
63 CachedResource::finishLoading(data, metrics);
64}
